﻿App Link on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.encurate.brintonmuseum.
Application Name: The Brinton Museum.
Number of Reviews: .
Application Description: Learn more about The Brinton Museum with our app!  App tours of the museum include detailed information about the collection that is unavailable elsewhere.  The app will locate where you are on the Quarter Circle A Ranch property and guide you to important sites.  Enjoy doing the “Hunt for the Horned Toads” scavenger hunt as you stroll around the grounds.  Walk the Nature Trail and learn more about area birds and wildlife.  We’ve also included a schedule of events at The Brinton and information on our shows and exhibits.Read moreCollapse.
